attachments.title: DIMPLE.IO - your custom Android NFC buttons!
attachments.text: DIMPLE™ is a protective case or little sticker with four or two user configurable buttons for Android™ NFC™ devices. You are the one who chooses the button functionality. It makes doing everyday tasks a lot more quicker and saves your precious time.
